6:   - Then: Returns matching sessions\n237: \n238: - [ ] **TEST-023**: `TestRedisStore_ListByUser`\n239:   - Given: Sessions for multiple users in Redis\n240:   - When: ListByUser() called\n241:   - Then: Returns sessions for specified user\n242: \n243: - [ ] **TEST-024**: `TestRedisStore_ConnectionFailure`\n244:   - Given: Invalid Redis address\n245:   - When: NewRedisStore() called\n246:   - Then: Returns error\n247: \n248: - [ ] **TEST-025**: `TestRedisStore_KeyExpiration`\n249:   - Given: Session with short TTL\n250:   - When: TTL expires\n251:   - Then: Session automatically removed\n252: \n253: #### Unit Tests - Session Manager\n254: \n255: - [ ] **TEST-030**: `TestSessionManager_CreateSession` in `pkg/router/session/manager_test.go`\n256:   - Given: Configured SessionManager\n257:   - When: CreateSession() called\n258:   - Then: Session created, stored, metrics recorded\n259: \n260: - [ ] **TEST-031**: `TestSessionManager_GetSession`\n261:   - Given: Existing session\n262:   - When: GetSession() called\n263:   - Then: Session returned, LastActivityAt updated\n264: \n265: - [ ] **TEST-032**: `TestSessionManager_GetSession_Expired`\n266:   - Given: Expired session\n267:   - When: GetSession() called\n268:   - Then: Returns ErrSessionExpired, session cleaned up\n269: \n270: - [ ] **TEST-033**: `TestSessionManager_DeleteSession`\n271:   - Given: Existing session\n272:   - When: DeleteSession() called\n273:   - Then: Session removed, metrics recorded\n274: \n275: - [ ] **TEST-034**: `TestSessionManager_ListSessions`\n276:   - Given: Multiple sessions\n277:   - When: ListSessions() with filters\n278:   - Then: Returns matching sessions\n279: \n280: - [ ] **TEST-035**: `TestSessionManager_CleanupExpiredSessions`\n281:   - Given: Mix of active and expired sessions\n282:   - When: CleanupExpiredSessions() called\n283:   - Then: Only expired sessions removed, count returned\n284: \n285: - [ ] **TEST-036**: `TestSessionManager_SessionAffinity`\n286:   - Given: Session 